                        <interp inst="t18350706-name-431" type="surname" value="EARLES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350706-name-431" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD EARLES</persName>
                  </hi>. I live next door to John Giles's shop in Shoreditch. On the 3rd of July I saw the prisoner looking in at the window—I watched, and saw him enter the shop, and return with this parcel of goods, which he put into the apron of his companion, and ran away—I pursued and caught hold of his arm—he dropped these goods, and I took them up—the prisoner was taken within a minute afterwards—I am sure he is the person.</p>
